node.text:
GIVEAWAY! We have teamed up with our friends @salishancoastallodge to give away 2 FREE nights at Salishan Coastal Lodge!

Not ready for summer to end? Escape to the Oregon Coast and celebrate second summer at Salishan Coastal Lodge. Nestled between Gleneden Beach, Siletz Bay and the Oregon Coastal Range, you're invited to soak in the wild air and enjoy room to roam. The lodge is home to the Oregon Coast's only Aerial Park, a Championship seaside golf course, and a peaceful and relaxing spa with views overlooking Siletz Bay.

For your chance to win this incredible experience, make sure you’re following @salishancoastallodge and tag some friends below! The more the better. One lucky winner will be randomly selected on Monday, August 23rd. Good luck!
